{"tid":1453674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"RTHK：示威女子右眼遭布袋彈射傷　眼科醫生稱或未必能保留眼球","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T10:08:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2d4683e937785f76f3caa2263e5e7493e2fad6","tid":1453674,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1474140_1_L_20190812125140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1474140_1_L_20190812125140.jpg&h=85aa96e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474140-20190812.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474140-20190812.htm&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpKVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=81aa3188\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474140-20190812.htm&h=964ffdbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474140-20190812.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀警署外昨日再有警民衝突，一名女子右眼受傷血流披面。有傳媒拍攝現場遺下一個被布袋彈打穿右邊外殼的眼罩。有醫生估計，傷者要復原部分視力的機會都較低，日後可能會變成大細眼，甚至未必能保留眼球。<br />\n<br />\n根據傷者入院時的消息，傷者眼球破裂、鞏膜破裂、數塊骨有骨折。眼科專科醫生龐朝輝相信，傷者眼部承受了很大力度。他說俗稱「眼白」的鞏膜，可能是被外物刺穿，亦可能是受壓過多，在眼球後方較薄的位置爆開，可以令視網膜脫落出血、甚至湧出，主要是盡快止血、修補撕裂位置。<br />\n<br />\n龐朝輝又說，骨折的碎骨可能進入眼球，需要清除，如果骨折嚴重，亦有可能壓住眼球後的神經線，眼腔的骨可能要重組。<br />\n<br />\n急症科專科醫生鄺葆賢則說，被任何子彈射中，除了眼部受傷，亦可能導致腦出血和骨折，視乎面骨碎裂的程度，有可能毀容。"},{"pid":"49ea56f8b877e182ca1ccb76bcc96aff06a155d3","tid":1453674,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:57:20.000Z","msg":"721811"},{"pid":"82223a3f4305483dd7c826aed7eec1c7165aa3ed","tid":1453674,"uid":153329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"黑社會冇一個是無辜的"},{"pid":"022b5e8c000eb426208c75c98674612b5ab8de1a","tid":1453674,"uid":142965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:59:23.000Z","msg":"[和理非升級] 全民跳閘不合作運動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1453593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1453593</a>"},{"pid":"e4ac05286ed0805b7bc3ee91dafc63dee9c81ede","tid":1453674,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:59:43.000Z","msg":"以眼還眼   屌你老母"},{"pid":"bdd17dbb034061f1b38c79711ad507a712c2b143","tid":1453674,"uid":235025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:07:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33c5d8b49069d6aa7301ee3b35b412faad28ea0b","tid":1453674,"uid":42149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"寧願大細眼都唔好失明丫。<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n天佑義士"},{"pid":"d03daecd61acb6bd0905e6e571c3b37990cc983d","tid":1453674,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLEooS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLEooS.png&h=4b443cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxZmxjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxZmxjw.png&h=1d33d451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g1fEi4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg1fEi4i.png&h=ea27d434&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"204b8564b045b74ae09ca21b5c18077c459decf0","tid":1453674,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:11:37.000Z","msg":"大家唔升級<br />\n就會令義士受傷及被捕"},{"pid":"175c479fd4d92e8e094a3cccebe8e7d6ff02e8ef","tid":1453674,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:18:45.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母<br />\n死港共走狗 仲想屈返落示威者到！"},{"pid":"75e77a5b43c88072cd5df8dd51a950ba3d3e42d3","tid":1453674,"uid":85498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i